div.div: Regression coefficients of the top models describing great tit local recruitment in relation to hatching date.
div.p: The regression coefficients (SE) for the top models (Delta QAICc <2) describing local recruitment of the willow tit in relation to centred hatching date from S3 Table. Coefficients are presented in the logit scale. Variables that had confidence intervals that do not include zero are in bold.
